HEADWORD: Epiornis
<hw>Ep`i*or"nis</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[NL.: cf. F.
<ets>⟦eacute⟧piornis</ets>. See <er>⟦AE⟧pyornis</er>.]</ety>
<fld>(Zo⟦oum⟧l.)</fld> <def>One of the gigantic ostrichlike birds of the
genus <gen>⟦AE⟧piornis</gen>, only recently extinct. Its remains have
been found in Madagascar.</def> <altsp>[Written also
<asp>⟦AE⟧pyornis</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

